siteMetadata.about:
I am a Software Engineer with over a year of experience, currently working at Walmart. I love building innovative and impactful products with a primary focus on writing clean, efficient, scalable code. Though primarily interested in Backend development and architecture, I love exploring other fields and have done projects across Full-stack development, Deep Learning and Robotics.
Get in touch at anshulsoodnet@gmail.com if you have an exciting opportunity or want to collaborate on a project.
